    "description": "A Postman collection for the Twitch Helix API, providing access to users, streams, games, clips, and follows. Uses https://api.twitch.tv/helix/ as the base URL. Requires OAuth 2.0 access token and Client ID from https://dev.twitch.tv/console. JSON responses. Free tier offers 800 rate limit points/minute as of August 2025. Users must set up OAuth flow in Postman or provide a valid access token.",
